node.text:
I've been looking for one place to charge the Mac, iPad, iPhone and AirPods that (importantly) doesn't look too cluttered.

What I've found isn't just a multi-device charger, it's also an extremely aesthetic way to organize your personal Apple ecosystem and desk setup. Check it out in-depth in the latest video!

Check out my latest video where I get into my thoughts on the M1 inside this particular design, the colors (don't pick wrong!), the chin, who I think will love this and who should wait and lots more!
